Plugins/Macros aside, wikis are limited in their syntax/markup (for obvious reasons). As such, customising rendering may not be possible for all cases compared to other documentation/markups forms (such as docbook with stylesheeting for the handbook).

However, it may be possible to achieve a similar effect using:

a) Admonitions, but use of these should be limited in most cases. See Also: https://moinmo.in/HelpOnMoinWikiSyntax#Admonitions

or

b)

{{{
quote
